First, we will show any homomorphism `f : R ‚Üí+* S` is well-defined as a map `R ‚ßł (ker f) ‚Üí+* S`.

Try filling in the missing proof using `intro`, `rw`, `apply` and/or `exact`.
-/

section universal_property
variable {S} [CommRing S]

def kerLift (f : R ‚Üí+* S) : R ‚ßł (ker f) ‚Üí+* S :=
  Ideal.Quotient.lift (ker f) f fun x ‚Ü¶ by
  intro h
  rw [mem_ker] at h
  exact h
